SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4940
A bill to amend 1994 PA 451, entitled
"Natural resources and environmental protection act,"
by amending sections 21502, 21503, 21506a, and 21510 (MCL
324.21502, 324.21503, 324.21506a, and 324.21510), sections 21502,
21503, and 21510 as amended by 2016 PA 380 and section 21506a as
amended by 2017 PA 134; and to repeal acts and parts of acts.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
