16
1 (a) The administrator determines, or the owner or operator
2 demonstrates to the satisfaction of the administrator, that 2 or
3 more confirmed releases are the result of a continuing or repeated
4 exposure from an initial eligible confirmed release.
5 (b) The releases described under subdivision (a) are
6 discovered during the same claim period.
7 (c) The releases described under subdivision (a) are not
8 interrupted or replaced by a separate cause.
9 (6) Expenses related to corrective actions taken to address a
10 confirmed release and that are part of an approved claim are
11 eligible for reimbursement and are subject to that approved claim's
